            </a>
            <div class="media-body">
              <h4 class="media-heading">Long Term Goals and Related Uses</h4>
              Allow researchers to go from medical imaging data to hemodynamic (blood flow) simulation results for patient specific models. The application, which integrates custom open-source code and best-in-class open source packages, includes an integrated flow solver with special outflow boundary conditions and fluid-structure interaction capabilities. This package has also been applied in simulations of medical devices, respiratory flows, and cardiac development.
            </div>
